                            <div class="txt">
                                <div class="hdr">
                                    <h4><a href="http://www.hepcomotion.com.cn/latest-news/hepcomtion%e6%94%b6%e8%b4%ad%e4%ba%86%e8%87%aa%e5%8a%a8%e5%8c%96%e4%b8%93%e4%b8%9a%e5%8e%82%e5%95%86-severn-automation/" title="HEPCOMTION收购了自动化专业厂商-SEVERN AUTOMATION">HEPCOMTION收购了自动化专业厂商-SEVERN AUTOMATION</a></h4>  
                                </div>
                                <div class="excerpt">
                                    <p>HEPCOMTION, 是世界领先的线性产品制造商，收购了自动化专业厂商-SEVERN AUTOMATION 将重新命名为HEPCOAUTO... <a href="http://www.hepcomotion.com.cn/latest-news/hepcomtion%e6%94%b6%e8%b4%ad%e4%ba%86%e8%87%aa%e5%8a%a8%e5%8c%96%e4%b8%93%e4%b8%9a%e5%8e%82%e5%95%86-severn-automation/">阅读更多</a></p>
                                </div>                                
                            </div>       
